Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\1c&HE0E0E0&\blur3}宇宙:阻止世界末日{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}创世之初 冥冥之中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the beginning, there was darkness...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}随着轰的一声{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then, bang...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}诞生了无限膨胀的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}时间 空间和物质{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of time, space, and matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在 所见超乎我们的想象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}超越了我们生存的限制{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}beyond the limits of our existence...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个空间我们称之为"宇宙"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in a place we call "The Universe."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}听起来宛如好莱坞大片:{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It sounds like a Hollywood blockbuster:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一颗致命小行星正在撞向地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a deadly asteroid is on a collision course with Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是在现实中 真有一颗巨大的世界末日大石头{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But in reality, is there a giant doomsday rock...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}威胁着要抹去文明吗?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that threatens to wipe out civilization?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是会不会发生的问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's not a question of if it'll happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而是何时会发生的问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's a question of when it will happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小行星在6500万年前抹去了恐龙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}An asteroid took out the dinosaurs 65 million years ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}下来轮到我们了吗?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Are we next?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}着手搜索这些宇宙杀手{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Go in search of these cosmic killers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}评估它们的威胁{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}assess their threat...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:01:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}分析最佳方法 在它们遭遇我们之前去截获它们{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and analyze the best ways to get them before they get us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}《阻止世界末日》从现在抓起{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}"Stopping Armageddon" starts now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它来自火星和木星之间的小行星带的某个地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It came from somewhere in the asteroid belt...between Mars and Jupiter...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一大堆碎石翻滚着{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a massive pile of rock and rubble...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大摇大摆一路奔向地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}rotating and rumbling its way towards Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}昔日大爆炸所产生的残骸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What was once mere debris from the Big Bang...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在注定要制造其自身的大爆炸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is now destined to make a big bang of its own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}突然闯入地球的大气层{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Bursting through the Earth's atmosphere...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个巨大的小行星会变成不可阻挡的力量{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}this giant asteroid becomes an unstoppable force.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:02:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其威力是苏联的"帝王核弹"的200万倍{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Nearly two million times more powerful...than the Soviet "Emperor Bomb"...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是史上引爆过的规模和威力最大的核装置{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the largest, most powerful explosive device ever detonated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它的目标是 洛杉矶{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Its target? Los Angeles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}人们最后一眼看到的是火光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The last thing anyone there sees is a flash...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}火球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a fireball...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后...{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果这颗小行星如我们设想的大如{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}lf this asteroid were as large as we might imagine...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}直径10公里的小行星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a 10-kilometer asteroid...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们认为撞击坑将会大上10倍{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we would be talking about a crater that is ten times larger than that...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们认为会有50英里的撞击坑{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}so we'd be talking about a 50-mile crater.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此整个洛杉矶将最终会变成这巨大的陨石坑{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So all of Los Angeles would end up being this humongous crater.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们认为绝对是毁灭性的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We'd be talking about absolute devastation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}100英里范围内的东西将荡然无存{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}nothing left over a range up to perhaps 100 miles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}远处的圣地亚哥 都会感到有强烈的地震{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}As far away as San Diego, they would get massive Earthquakes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}都会受到巨大的气浪冲击{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They would get massive air blasts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}狂风荡平200英里外的一切{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Winds that would simply flatten everything 200 miles away...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}将会伤及1000英里范围内的一切{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}would kill everything out to a range of perhaps 1,000 miles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那还只是直接的影响{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And that's just the immediate impact.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}随后你会看到整个碎片坠落回地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Then you would have all this debris fall back on the planet Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}将会像圣诞树那样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It'd be like a Christmas tree...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}看到所有的装饰品向四面八方抛洒出来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}seeing all these ornaments being thrown out in all directions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}于是你会看到大爆发{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then you would see firestorms...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大地熊熊燃烧{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}enormous areas of the planet Earth burning...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}释放出大量的烟尘{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}releasing even more soot and ash in the air...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}遮天蔽日{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}blanketing out sunlight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}温度骤降{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Temperatures would then plunge...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}生命将会被消灭{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and life itself would be perhaps extinguished.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你所看到的是严重的地球撞击事件的最坏的情景{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What you've just seen is a worst-case scenario...of a major Earth impact event.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可以消灭大部分地球生命{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The kinds of asteroids that can extinguish much of the life on Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大部分物种的各种小行星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}most of the species...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}约每一亿年左右光顾一次{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}come around every, say, hundred million years or so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它不是周期性现象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And it's not a periodic phenomenon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}并不会每一亿年发生一次{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It doesn't happen every hundred million years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它随时都会发生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It could happen at any time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只是平均起来 大约每一亿年一次{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Just on average, roughly once every hundred million years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此不是会不会发生的问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So it's not a question of if it'll happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而是何时发生的问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's a question of when it will happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小行星和彗星一直在撞击地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Asteroids and comets have been crashing into the Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要存在着地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}for as long as there's been an Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在诞生后不久{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Soon after its formation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}约四 五十亿年前{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}about four and a half billion years ago...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们的星球就成为了宇宙射击场里被频繁光顾的目标{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}our planet became a frequent target in a cosmic shooting gallery.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小行星和彗星为早期的地球带来了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Asteroids and comets brought to the early Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大部分的有机物质和水{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}much of the organic materials and water...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让生命得以形成{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that allowed life to form.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}后来的撞击{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Subsequent collisions...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}像6500万年前抹去恐龙的那一个{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}like the one that took out the dinosaurs 65 million years ago...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打断了演化{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}punctuated evolution...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让最具适应力的物种 那就是我们{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}allowing the most adaptable species-- that's us--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}登上了食物链的顶端{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to rise to the top of the food chain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此 我们应当将我们的存在和处境{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So we owe our very existence and our position...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}归功于有时会造成威胁的那些物体{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to these objects that sometimes cause a threat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}根据地球撞击数据库{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}According to the Earth Impact Database...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有160多个陨石坑得到了证实{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}more than 160 impact craters have been identified.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最大的叫做希克苏鲁伯{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The largest one is called Chicxulub...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}玛雅语中的"魔鬼的尾巴"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Mayan for "tail of the devil."{\r}
