Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}飓风 地震 诸如此类的东西{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}hurricanes or earthquakes or things like that--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那些原则上是可以预防的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is that, in principle, it's preventable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此你的工作未必就是如何去善后{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So your job isn't necessarily how do you clean up in the aftermath...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而是如何去预防它{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but how do you prevent it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是一个重大的区别{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and that's an important distinction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}预防大规模的地球撞击{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Preventing a massive Earth impact...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把我们带到了阻止世界末日的第二步:{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}brings us to step two for stopping Armageddon:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}缓解{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}mitigation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让致命的近地物体失效谈何容易{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Neutralizing a deadly near-Earth object is no easy task.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它来自好莱坞{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Take it from Hollywood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}亦或不行{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Or maybe not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最糟糕的做法尽在好莱坞电影里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The worst thing to do is to look at all the Hollywood movies...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们看到猛男走出航天飞机{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where we have macho men going out in the space shuttle...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来到深太空 将氢弹放到那些物体上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}way out in deep space, planting hydrogen bombs on these objects.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯 首先 航天飞机甚至都到不了那个距离{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, first of all, the space shuttle can't even reach those distances.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}航天飞机只能够围绕着地球本身运转{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The space shuttle simply goes around the planet Earth itself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其次 更重要的是{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Second of all, and more important...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}炸毁小行星是最糟糕的方案{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to blow up an asteroid is the worst possible scenario.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为没有了一颗大型小行星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}'Cause instead of having one monster asteroid...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你现在则有了两个 三个 或四个碎片{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}you now have two, three, four pieces...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}每一块都足以对地球发起巨大的撞击{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}each piece capable of initiating tremendous havoc on the planet Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}另一方面 如果它是个大型物体{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}On the other hand, if it were a large object...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你就有足够的时间 若干年的时间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and you had enough time, several years...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你可以尝试去炸毁它{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}you could try and blow it up...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}希望弹片能避开地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and hope that the shrapnel would miss the Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}至少大部分能避开{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or most of it would.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不过对于大物体 我们几乎能提前发现的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But large objects we almost certainly would find ahead of time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}实际上众多小物体{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's really the small, far more numerous objects...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}才是难以对付的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that are the ones that are tough to deal with.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果彻底摧毁{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If outright destruction...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如好莱坞式的炸毁 太冒险了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}such as a Hollywood-style bombing, is too risky...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或者充其量 只保留最大的小行星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or, at best, reserved for only for the largest asteroids...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}更为保险的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}there's a safer way...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是将近地物体移出危害的路径{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to move a near-Earth object out of harm's way...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那就是偏离{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and that's by deflection.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果小行星一头撞向地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}lf an asteroid is headed toward an impact with Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你最好是极其轻微地改变其轨道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}you're far better off by changing its orbit very slightly...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这样让它避开地球 呆在一个地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}so that it misses the Earth, but stays in one piece...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要好过你试图炸毁它{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}much better off than you are trying to break it up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你无法让任何物体消失殆尽{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You can't make anything disappear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你只能将它炸成碎片{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You simply break it into pieces.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}轰炸它将会将它炸成碎片{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Bombing it is going to break it into pieces...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}将会造成更多的破坏{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}which could do much more damage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那会是霰弹攻击来代替步枪子弹{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's a shotgun blast instead of a rifle bullet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要效果最佳 偏离则需要尽可能的提前量{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}To work best, deflection requires as much lead time as possible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}数年 甚至数十年{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Years, if not decades.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}简而言之 早发现意味着早偏离{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Put simply, early detection means early deflection.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}尤为重要的是 它越远{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}More importantly, the farther away it is...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们所要施加的力量就越小{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the less force we have to apply...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}以导致小行星轨道的大转移{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in order to cause a large shift in the asteroid's orbit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为了证明这一点 我们来玩一下冰球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}To demonstrate the point, let's play hockey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}球员击球距离球门越远{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The further away from the net a player shoots the puck...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}阻挡目标所需的偏离也就越小{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the less deflection will be needed to prevent a goal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而 如果球员射门越靠近球门{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}However, if a player takes a shot much closer to the net...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那么就需要更大的偏离{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}then a much larger deflection is required...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让冰球转向{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to keep the puck from going in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在来设想一下 那冰球是颗小行星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now imagine that the puck is an asteroid...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}球门是地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the net is the Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}首选方案{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The preferred scenarios...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是通过改变其速度来偏离小行星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}are to deflect the asteroid by changing its velocity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我们进行偏离有足够的提前量{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}lf we can do that sufficiently far in advance...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比方说 10年{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}for example, ten years...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们就只需要改变其速度不足每秒一厘米{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we only need to change its velocity less than one centimeter per second.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此这是速度上的极其微小的改变{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So it's a very, very small change in velocity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}于是其累积效应将意味着{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The cumulative effect then will mean...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它将会抵达的地方 既不是在我们的前方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that it will get to where we are either before we are there...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或地球所处位置的后方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or after the Earth is at that position...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此将不再是个问题了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}so it is no longer a problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要做到这一点 几个偏转策略已经提出{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}To do just that, several deflection strategies have been proposed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}要说声对不起布鲁斯.威利斯了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And with apologies to Bruce Willis...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}丝毫不需要载人飞行{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}none requires a manned mission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}事实上 载人飞行将极大地妨碍那些东西{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In fact, a manned mission would significantly hinder these things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对此 利用目前的技术和目前的航天器{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}To this point, with current technology and current vehicles...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们实际上无法跑得离地球很远{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we can't really get very far away from the Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那将严重制约你的能力{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and that severely constrains your ability...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去真正解决其中的一个问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to actually solve one of these problems...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果最佳时间可能是到太阳的对面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}when the optimal time might be the opposite side of the Sun...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去造访小行星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to meet the asteroid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}法国研究人员提出的一个偏离策略{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One deflection strategy advanced by French researchers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}叫做征用无威胁的小行星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}calls for commandeering a non-threatening asteroid...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}将近地物体敲离轨道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to knock an Earth-bound object off course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个策略可谓是"以星制星"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Call this strategy "asteroid versus asteroid."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它并非是天方夜谭{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's not totally outside the realm of possibility.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}尝试将它停泊在我们想要的地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Trying to park it where we want it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不让它撞击地球是问题的要害{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and not have it hit the Earth is in itself questionable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们只有其中的某些处在地球的附近{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We have only a certain number of these...that are anywhere near the Earth.{\r}
